HEADWORD: Sentine
<hw>Sen"tine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sentina</ets> bilge water, hold of a ship, dregs: cf. F.
<ets>sentine</ets>.]</ety> <def>A place for dregs and dirt; a sink; a
